README
------

The files in this folder are Mustache template files (HTML) for JS.

A template-file can be retrieved as a hash array splitted on ###
with each template assigned to a template-name:

vrtxAdmin.retrieveHTMLTemplates(fileName,
                                ["<template-name-1", ..., "<template-name-n>"],
                                deferred);
                                
E.g. for frontpage-boxes:

var templatesRetrieved = $.Deferred();
vrtxAdmin.retrieveHTMLTemplates("templates",
                                ["string", "html", "radio", "dropdown", "date", "browse", "add-remove-move"],
                                templatesRetrieved);

To make HTML with the array:

var html = $.mustache(templates["<assigned-template-name>"], JSON-object);

The properties of the JSON-object is outputted with {{ }} around it
in the template-file.

Se more documentation of template writing:

https://github.com/janl/mustache.js
http://mustache.github.com/mustache.5.html
